      "source_code": "public interface IDataFrame\n{\n\tobject this[int columnIndex] { get; }\n\n\tint ColumnsCount { get; }\n\n\tstring? Name { get; set; }\n\n\tint RowCount { get; }\n\n\tint AddColumn(DataFrameColumn dataFrameColumn);\n\n\tint AddColumn(DataFrameColumn dataFrameColumn, bool bypassColumnShrink);\n\n\tvoid AddRow(params object[] items);\n\n\tTask AddRowsFromColumnRowArrayAsync(object[][] items);\n\n\tvoid Append(IDataFrame dataFrame);\n\n\tstring[] GetAllColumnsNames();\n\n\tDataFrameColumn GetColumn(int columnOrdinal);\n\n\tint GetColumnOrdinal(string name);\n\n\tobject[] GetRowArray(int rowIndex);\n\n\tT GetValue<T>(int columnOrdinal, int rowIndex);\n\n\tobject GetValueAsObject(int columnOrdinal, int rowIndex);\n\n\tvoid Optimize();\n\n\tstring Peek(int maxRecords = 1000);\n\n\tTask<MemoryStream> GetParquetStreamAsync();\n\n\tTask<byte[]?> GetParquetByteArrayAsync();\n\n\tDataSet ToDataSet();\n\n\tDataTable ToDataTable();\n\n\tobject[][] ToRowsArray();\n}"
